text: Went for laser treatments to get rid of the freckles on my face. Dr Winston is very patient and attentive. Got very obvious improvement after one treatment. Transparent pricing (price list is available on their website)
Dr Winston Lin is patient and detailed in his explanation. My husband also saw the improvement in my complexion after the treatment and he also joined me. ☺️
Dr Winston is very patient and takes care to explain how Botox jaw slimming works. Will definitely make an appointment to visit him again!
